      "note": "Grocery prices remain excluded while chain-source collection is unreliable. This board now includes currently visible food items from the supplier price-source sites and skips out-of-stock or non-food listings."
    },
    "methodology": [
      "Every item must have a public source link, a visible price, and a unit or package basis.",
      "Manual status means the public price was captured from a supplier page but does not yet have a purpose-built parser.",
      "Supplier items are not always like-for-like comparisons; package size, pickup, shipping, and subscription terms matter.",
      "Grocery-chain prices will return only after collection is reliable enough to avoid publishing blocked or stale values."
